    <section class="content-section" id="introduction">
        <h2>AI for Effective Humanitarian Action</h2>
        <p>In a world increasingly defined by rapid change and complex challenges, the need for effective humanitarian action is more critical than ever. At the forefront of this pursuit is artificial intelligence, offering innovative solutions to aid those in need.</p>
        
